 agoand is 'deeply ashamed' of her actionsbut is still awaiting her tribunal to discover the length of any potential ban.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'error\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"four years agoand\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"her tribunal\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the length\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"any potential ban\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Months after the scandal broke, the Brit is still said to be reeling from the after-effects which include continued death threats and abuse for her actions.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scandal\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the after-effects\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"continued death threats\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"her actions\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Mentally they are crucifying her,' an anonymous rider who rides at the same yard as Dujardin toldThe Times.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an anonymous rider\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the same yard\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin toldThe Times\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She's got antis [anti-hunt saboteurs] outside the house, death threats.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"antis\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-hunt saboteurs\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ng